    "description": "S.T. Corporation manufactures and sells deodorizers and air fresheners, mothproofing agents, gloves, dehumidifiers, and other products in Japan and internationally. The company primarily offers air fresheners under the Shoshu-Riki brand; deodorizers under the Dashu-Tan Charcoal brand; mothproofing agents under the Mushuda and Neopara ace brands; disposable warmers under the Onpax and On Style brands; household gloves under the Family brand; and dehumidifiers under the Drypet brand. It also offers pet supplies under Nyantomo Clean Toilet brand; rice bug repellents under Kometoban brand. The company was formerly known as S.T. Chemical Co., Ltd. and changed its name to S.T. Corporation in 2007. S.T. Corporation was incorporated in 1948 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
